IF EXISTS ( SELECT * FROM sys.external_tables WHERE object_id = OBJECT_ID('dbo.T_STManualJournals') )
    DROP EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STManualJournals
GO

CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE dbo.T_STManualJournals (
[sap_journalsheader_postingdate] datetime2(7),
[sap_journalsheader_duedate] datetime2(7),
[sap_journalsheader_doctotal] numeric(18,2),
[sap_journalsheader_doctype] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsheader_transid] int,
[sap_journalsline_linenum] int,
[sap_journalsline_acctcode] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsheader_objtype] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_project] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_vatgroup] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_vatrate] numeric(18,2),
[sap_journalsline_vatamount] numeric(18,2),
[sap_journalsline_description] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_jnlref1] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_jnlref2] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_subdepotcode] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_linetotal] numeric(18,2),
[sap_journalsline_doccat] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsline_itemcode] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsheader_cardcode] nvarchar(4000),
[sap_journalsheader_cardref] nvarchar(4000),


	)
	WITH (
	LOCATION = 'Structured Data/FINANCE/stmanualjournals.parquet',
	DATA_SOURCE = [synapse_citylogisticsstorage_dfs_core_windows_net],
	FILE_FORMAT = [SynapseParquetFormat]
	)
GO


SELECT TOP 100 * FROM dbo.T_STManualJournals 
GO
